<P>
   &UR; EDITORS: With Halloween just around the corner, The New York Times
Syndicate offers your readers ideas for four simple-to-make
costumes for kids. Terrific photos of all four costumes available.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; GREAT COSTUMES WITH LITTLE FUSS &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (600 words) &QL; 
 &UR; By KATHY SENA &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   How about a new twist on the traditional ghost costume: spooky
sound effects? Sena offers three other possibilities for
treat-or-treating garb _ a pair of dice, a flower and a scarecrow _
with a list of materials and easy directions for all. (slugged:
