   Orr, senior editor of the Children's Software Revue newsletter,
offers recommendations on what computers, printers, phone equipment
and software are best for home offices. In an accompanying sidebar,
she lists some of the online resources designed for small and
home-based businesses. (slugged:
BC-EQUIPPING-HOME-OFFICES-(HOME-BUSINESS-WEEK)-NYTSF, priority code
r, category code l and b) &QL;
