<HEADLINE>
WHITTIER IS OUT, BUT MILES DAVIS IS IN  
 (WITH CANON) 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By RICHARD NILSEN  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
