<DOCNO> NYT19981021.0175 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-21 15:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9123 &Cx1f; tic-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MRSCASTANEDA-AZR &LR;      10-21 1575
