<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-21 17:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9508 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CIR-COLLECTING-ART-63     10-21 0996
</HEADER>
