<P>
   UNDATED _ Before I tell you why boxer Mike Tyson deserves to be
back in the ring, I have a confession to make. Because I've long
been a pacifist, and have a general reputation of being against
violence, people tend to be very surprised when they learn two
things about me. I'm a fan of boxing, and I love bullfights. Don't
say it, because I've heard it all. And animal lovers, please don't
send any literature because I've seen it all. By BOB RAY SANDERS.
