   TERRORIST-CIRCLE (Undated) _ After the embassy bombings, a new
look at the Brooklyn militants who figured in not only in the World
Trade Center case, but also in the 1990 assassination of Rabbi Meir
Kahane and the 1993 conspiracy to blow up the United Nations and
other New York City landmarks. The article was reported by Benjamin
