<SLUG> BC-CASTRO-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Lawmakers seek punishment for Castro
 &HT;    By Arthur Brice
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA -- Many Cuban-Americans say they want Fidel Castro to
suffer the same fate that befell former Chilean dictator Augusto
Pinochet, who is in British custody in connection with the deaths
of several Spaniards during his 17-year rule.
